<h2>Hi, I am <span class="textAccent">Geert</span></h2>
<p>My name is Geert Roks. I am currently enrolled in the bachelors Music and Technology at the University of Arts Utrecht (HKU). There I am specializing in Creative Systems Design with focus on Digital Signal Processing and Music Information Retrival. Here I can combine two of my big passions: music and science.</p>
